text: Ram Surat Prasad (born 9 February 1925) is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Lok Sabha, the lower house of the Parliament of India from the Bansgaon constituency of Uttar Pradesh as a member of the Indian National Congress. ==References== ==External links== *Official biographical sketch in Parliament of India website Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Indian National Congress politicians Category:Lok Sabha members from Uttar Pradesh Category:5th Lok Sabha members
title: Ram Surat Prasad
